# Ticket 003 – Application Access Issue

## Incident Summary
User reported inability to access a business application required for daily operations.

## User Impact
User unable to complete work tasks requiring the application.

## Environment
Windows 10 workstation connected to corporate network.

## Troubleshooting Performed
- Verified network connectivity
- Confirmed user authentication successful
- Restarted application
- Checked application configuration settings
- Cleared cached credentials
- Tested login using a new application session

## Findings
Application configuration file appeared corrupted causing authentication failure.

## Root Cause
Corrupted application configuration.

## Resolution / Action Taken
Application configuration reset and application restarted.  
User confirmed successful access.

